    <questiontext format="html">
      <text><![CDATA[<p class="HELM_exercise">Exercise</p>
<p>Find the equations of the tangent and normal lines to the following curves at the points indicated.<br><br> </p>
<p> </p>
<ol class="HELM_parts">
    <li>\(y = {@f1@}, \text{ at } ({@x0@}, {@y0@})\)
        <p>Give all numerical values as&nbsp;<strong>precise values</strong>.</p>
        <p>Tangent line: \(y = \) [[input:ans1]] [[validation:ans1]] [[feedback:prt1]]</p>
        <p>Normal line: \(y = \) [[input:ans2]] [[validation:ans2]] [[feedback:prt2]]</p>
    </li>
    <p></p>
    <li>
        <p>\(y = \sqrt{1 - x^2}, \text{ at }\left(\dfrac{\sqrt{2}}{2}, \dfrac{\sqrt{2}}{2}\right)\)<br>Give all numerical values as <strong>precise values</strong>.<br></p>
        <p>Tangent line: \(y = \) [[input:ans3]] [[validation:ans3]] [[feedback:prt3]] </p>
        <p> Normal line: \(y = \) [[input:ans4]] [[validation:ans4]] [[feedback:prt4]]</p>
    </li>
    <p>
    </p>
    <li>\(y = {@f3@}, \text{ at } ({@x1@}, {@y1@})\)
        <p> Round all numerical values to <strong>2 decimal places</strong>. </p>
        <p> Tangent line: \(y = \) [[input:ans5]] [[validation:ans5]] [[feedback:prt5]]</p>
        <p> Normal line: \(y = \) [[input:ans6]] [[validation:ans6]] [[feedback:prt6]]</p>
    </li>
</ol>]]></text>
