      <text><![CDATA[<ol class="HELM_parts">
    <li> \(f(x) = {@f1@} \quad \frac{df}{dx} = {@diff(f1,x)@} \quad \frac{df}{dx}\bigg|_{{@x0@}} = {@m0@}.\)
        <p></p>
        <p>Tangent line \(y = {@m0@}x + c\). This passes through \(({@x0@}, {@y0@})\) so \(y = {@m0*x + c0@}.\)<br></p>
        <p>Normal line \(y = {@n0@}x + d\). This passes through \(({@x0@}, {@y0@})\) so \(y = {@n0*x + d0@}.\)</p>
    </li>
    <p>
    </p>
    <li> \(f(x) = \sqrt{1 - x^2} \quad \frac{df}{dx} = \frac{-x}{\sqrt{1 - x^2}} \quad \frac{df}{dx} \bigg|_{x_0} = -1.\)
        <p>Tangent line \(y = -x + c\). This passes through \((\frac{\sqrt{2}}{2}, \frac{\sqrt{2}}{2})\) so \(y = -x + \sqrt{2}.\) </p>
        <p>Normal line \(y = x + d\). This passes through \((\frac{\sqrt{2}}{2}, \frac{\sqrt{2}}{2})\) so \(y=x.\) </p>
        <p>
